Healthcare Management Backend - API Endpoints

AUTH POST /api/auth/register POST /api/auth/login POST /api/auth/logout
GET /api/auth/me

USERS GET /api/users/ GET /api/users/:id PATCH /api/users/:id DELETE
/api/users/:id

DOCTORS POST /api/doctors/create GET /api/doctors/ GET /api/doctors/:id
PATCH /api/doctors/:id PATCH /api/doctors/:id/approve DELETE
/api/doctors/:id

PATIENTS POST /api/patients/create GET /api/patients/ GET
/api/patients/:id PATCH /api/patients/:id DELETE /api/patients/:id

APPOINTMENTS POST /api/appointments/create GET /api/appointments/ GET
/api/appointments/:id PATCH /api/appointments/:id DELETE
/api/appointments/:id PATCH /api/appointments/:id/status

HEALTH RECORDS POST /api/records/create GET /api/records/ GET
/api/records/:id PATCH /api/records/:id DELETE /api/records/:id

PRESCRIPTIONS POST /api/prescriptions/create GET /api/prescriptions/ GET
/api/prescriptions/:id PATCH /api/prescriptions/:id DELETE
/api/prescriptions/:id

TESTS POST /api/tests/create GET /api/tests/ GET /api/tests/:id PATCH
/api/tests/:id DELETE /api/tests/:id POST /api/tests/:id/upload-report

UPLOADS POST /api/uploads/profile POST /api/uploads/aadhaar POST
/api/uploads/license POST /api/uploads/test-report

AUDIT LOGS GET /api/audits/ GET /api/audits/:id